# Bus Pass Management System

This project is a Bus Pass Management System built using PHP and Visual Studio 2022. It is designed to streamline the process of issuing, renewing, and managing bus passes for students at Sussex College.

## Features

- User authentication and authorization
- Issue new bus passes
- Renew existing bus passes
- Manage user information
- Admin panel for managing all operations

## Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/sanith531/bus-pass-management-system-for-sussex-college.git
   cd bus-pass-management-system

Set up your environment

Ensure you have PHP installed on your machine.
Set up a local server (e.g., XAMPP, WAMP).
Database Setup

Create a new database.
Import the database.sql file located in the db directory to set up the required tables.
Configure the application

Open the config.php file in the root directory and update the database configuration settings.
Run the application

Start your local server and navigate to https://github.com/sanith531/bus-pass-management-system-for-sussex-college.git.
Usage
Admin Login

Navigate to the admin login page and log in using admin credentials.
Manage bus passes, user information, and more from the admin panel.
User Registration/Login

New users can register for an account.
Existing users can log in to view and renew their bus passes.
Technologies Used
PHP
MySQL
HTML/CSS
